cleaned_text: The GW Center for Integrative Medicine proudly introduces its excellent team of highly qualified practitioners and staff. We are a team of passionate, caring, and experienced healthcare professionals who see each patient as a whole, and integrate our knowledge and experience to create a unique treatment plan for every healing journey. We meet every week to discuss our patients' medical cases, and to share the newest medical breakthroughs with each other and with the extended medical community.
